text_1.text: The transformer architecture revolutionized natural language processing through self-attention mechanisms.

text_2.text: Large language models exhibit emergent capabilities that scale with model size and training data.

text_3.text: Memory-efficient attention techniques enable deployment of massive neural networks on resource-constrained devices.
